{"tid":713041,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"非洲細路終於有飯開","createTime":"2018-06-22T14:02:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T14:07:37.000Z","uid":179547,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"90547ff89a0f408ab14fc3e427e9b324337acedb","tid":713041,"uid":179547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:02:01.000Z","msg":"美斯一直非常熱心慈善事業，根據西班牙的報道，世界杯期間他將會參加一項公益活動，他的每個入球都能為貧困地區的兒童帶來福音。<br />\n<br />\n據《馬卡報》報導，美斯此次參加的公益項目內容是：在俄羅斯世界杯上，美斯每入一球，就會為拉丁美洲與加勒比海地區的兒童捐贈1萬份學校午餐。該項目將通過聯合國世界糧食計劃署來進行，美斯和尼馬都是參與者。　<br />\n　<br />\n美斯表示：「我為能參與這項活動感到驕傲，這能夠幫助到我的國家和世界各地的兒童改善生活，我們想盡可能地讓孩子的臉上出現笑容。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">尼馬也表達對慈善事業的支持：「我們知道當我們團結起來，就能戰勝飢餓，這個項目就是很好的例子。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/220138_6d3499655d4f26e610aaf10f898f009a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F220138_6d3499655d4f26e610aaf10f898f009a.png&h=1918d2be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n都係要靠尼馬先開到飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b44f9b2bffdf08ce65e6b69fbff80ebb90ca91","tid":713041,"uid":10274,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:03:03.000Z","msg":"#抽水快係好不過要抽得準<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44500d27a975660d67a15ed40e4e11b88e45217a","tid":713041,"uid":34419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:03:24.000Z","msg":"Update下啦 old news<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdebb845b8afa6f332204ca176b602c0e7f2e0c7","tid":713041,"uid":48834,"li